songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Skrrt, skrrt
Skrrt (Skrrt), skrrt
Skrrt (Skrrt), skrrt
Skrrt, skrrt
Skrrt (Let's go, let's go)

[Verse 1]
Kick a bitch out, make her sleep on the floor
Run from the plug, nigga it's fuck what I owe
Smoking on dope shit, look like mould
Young nigga get that shit out the bowl
Never been on the run, only run on the road
Hit a nigga up, one shot, came close
Can't fuck with yall niggas, I know you gon' fold
Got your hand out, did this shit on my own
Back in the seat, packing the heat, back on my feet (Yeah, yeah)
Smashing your hoe, clapping them cheeks, showing them teeth, aye
Rollie on my wrist, don't tick, don't tock
God a bad little bitch, know the pussy gon' pop
Niggas know where I be, won't hide from no opp
Big drum in the Dray, won't need no Glock
Got a stick on me now, gon' run and get chopped

[Interlude]
Oh yeah (Huh), oh yeah, oh yeah

[Verse 2]
Yeah, running from the plug, yeah, straight like that
Drop down on a nigga, then hit four flat
Clean a nigga out, I ain't use their jet (Yeah)
Having too much dope, but I'm still gon' take (Money so long, so long)
I don't wanna fuck if their hair game wack (Hm)
Yeah, young ass nigga gon' ship them packs
He ain't never sold a brick, how the fuck he gon' rap (Hm)
I was really in the streets, late night, straight snatching
Bitch
songs.title: SKRRT
